00063 static void gob_cmcon(cmconpara* p,

00097 void calcConstraintCM(const SlaterDet* Q, const SlaterDetAux* X,
00098                       double* cmconstraint)
00099 {
00100   double xcm[3], pcm[3];
00101   OneBodyOperator op_ob_mx = {dim: 3, opt: 1, par: NULL, me: ob_mx};
00102   OneBodyOperator op_ob_p = {dim: 3, opt: 1, par: NULL, me: ob_p};
00103 
00104   calcSlaterDetOBME(Q, X, &op_ob_mx, xcm);
00105   calcSlaterDetOBME(Q, X, &op_ob_p, pcm);
00106 
00107   *cmconstraint = SQR(xcm[0])+SQR(xcm[1])+SQR(xcm[2])+
00108                   SQR(pcm[0])+SQR(pcm[1])+SQR(pcm[2]);
00109 
00110 
00111   // the donlp2 routine tries to sample unphysical states 
00112   // from time to time, punish that try
00113 
00114   if (isnan(*cmconstraint))
00115     *cmconstraint = 100000;
00116 
00117 }
